ProcessGHXUpdates is an ActionForm
    action is ProcessGHXUpdates
    Layout
        single column
            ContractGroup
            AutoUpdateContracts
        visible when (AutoUpdateContracts)
            single column
                LineUpdateOption
                    label is "OptionsToUpdateLinesWhenUpdatingContractDates"
                text of "OptionsWhenUpdatingLineCosts"
                    italics
            paragraph
                TolerancePercent
                Connector
                ToleranceAmount
                RejectAllCostIncreases
                    label is "ReviewAllItemsWithCostDifferences"
            single column
                ProcessItemMasterOnly
            two column
                UpdateCostsOnly
                text of "If_Update_Costs_OnlyIsSetToTrue;OnlyLinesWithUpdateFunctionSetToUpdateWillProcess;OnlyCostsWillBeUpdated,NotOtherFields"
                    italics
        single column
            text of "TheFollowingUpdatesMayBePerformed:_ItemCostChanges,NewItemAdditions,DeletionsOfItems,TierChanges"
                italics
            text of "NewMembers,ContractDateChanges,VendorItemChanges,DistributorMarkups,NewDistributors,ChangedSuppliers"
                italics
